  <section class="dual-care info-box centered-section">
    <h2>Functional &amp; Naturopathic Doctors — and Why We Suggest Both</h2>
    <p>We are not against medical doctors. The conventional medical system is designed to diagnose and treat symptoms — invaluable for acute care and serious diagnoses. We recommend <strong>both</strong>:</p>
    <ul class="bullets center-bullets">
      <li><strong>Have an MD/DO:</strong> diagnostics, imaging, prescriptions, and acute care.</li>
      <li><strong>Add a functional or naturopathic doctor:</strong> deeper labs, lifestyle, and nutrient-first strategies to address root causes.</li>
    </ul>

